item.title: Chatters that Matter, Celebrating Black History Month with Pioneer and Fantasy Author Gloria Sanders-Williams AKA Fire4Desire
item.description: Las Vegas, NV Gloria Sanders-Williams, aka Desire4Fire, grew up in the San Francisco/Bay Area, where at a young age, her exposure to a creative cultural mix inspired her imagination and writing. She began her writing career at sixteen with works that included short stories and poetry. She has recently branched out to evolve her work into a current love of performance poetry at venues throughout the Las Vegas area where she resides... item.description:
